+
+Status: `INFERRED`
+
+Tao's literal constants and formulas are part of one engineered realization,
+not the whole Step-1 object. What must survive is the hierarchy they encode:
+one channel exponentially weaker than the amplifier channel, a post-threshold
+amplifier and rotor response that dominates, and delayed next-stage transfer
+that becomes macroscopic only after the rotor stage.
+
+Later Tao-likeness tests are not honest if they preserve the graph but erase
+this ordered size hierarchy.
+
