+# The Tiny Trigger Role Is Dynamically Central
+
+Status: `VERIFIED`
+
+The tiny trigger `X3,n` is dynamically central while energetically negligible
+before threshold. It is the decisive variable that makes the delayed-threshold
+mechanism work.
+
+A candidate that lacks this tiny-trigger role may still resemble a sparse
+cascade, but it is not Tao-like in the inherited sense.
+
+Filed from:
+- `missions/exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit/library-inbox/step-001-exploration-001-feature-ledger.md`
