+# Helical-Sign Bookkeeping Is Load-Bearing For Later Exact-NS Audits
+
+Status: `INFERRED`
+
+The exact setting is Fourier-helical, and the surviving mismatch question is
+tied to geometry-fixed coefficients and helicity signs. Even before one final
+sign sheet is frozen, the branch must name and track helical signs canonically.
+
+Later exact-NS audits cannot test Tao-likeness honestly if sign information is
+left implicit or allowed to drift between equivalent-looking packet
+descriptions.
+
+Filed from:
