+# Literal ODE Coordinates, Coefficient Formulas, And Shell Packaging Are Dispensable
+
+Status: `INFERRED`
+
+The literal five-scalar ODE coordinates `(a,b,c,d,ã)`, Tao's exact numerical
+coefficient formulas, and a polished shell-cascade presentation are packaging
+choices rather than the Step-1 object itself.
+
+What must survive is the role ledger, delayed-threshold logic, ordered size
+hierarchy, and bookkeeping discipline. A Fourier-helical packet realization can
+still count as Tao-like if those load-bearing features remain intact.
+
+Filed from:
